title: The Taylor Swift Autographed Album WINNERS
description:
We are used to Taylor Swift winning album of the year every single time, but who will win an actual autographed album from the Queen herself? The 13 podcast had their very first contest in which two lucky and creative Swifties will win their very own autographed albums! The results are in and the winners are....
Thank you to everyone that participated! It was very hard to choose with all of the great entries. We hope to do many more giveaways in the future!
Thank you for your constant support! We appreciate you all!
